      "file_path": "docker_push_manifest.sh",
      "patchset_number": 15,
      "line": 24,
      "message": "Yes, once we have a final OK on the patch we will change that to \"onap\" (which is available, and linked to LF Jenkins). Currently we're keeping \"cristinapauna\" for testing the push part in sandbox.",
      "author": {
